<!--
README: How to customize this page
- To change the name shown in the hero:
  * Edit the <span class="hero-name">Huxel</span> element.
- To update the greeting or subtitle:
  * Edit the <h1 class="hero-greeting"> and <p class="hero-subtitle"> elements.
- To change role/title in About:
  * Edit the element <h3 class="role">Frond-End Developer</h3>.
- To add/remove skills:
  * Edit the "skills-grid" section â€” each skill is an article.skill-card.
- To update achievements:
  * Edit the .achievements-grid items â€” each .achievement has an <img> (or inline SVG), a heading, and a description.
- To change contact info and copy:
  * Edit the footer and the contact details in the Contact section.
- To provide your real CV file for "Download CV" button:
  * Place your CV at `assets/Huxel_CV.pdf` (or change the path in the JS download function).
- Assets:
  * Add images/icons under `assets/` and update image src paths.
- Fonts & colors:
  * Primary colors and fonts are controlled via CSS variables at the top of the CSS file (see the instructions in the CSS file).
-->
